=================
1) Login to OpenShift

Use oc login via FID

Ensure correct cluster access and permissions

2) Validate SMCP (Service Mesh Control Plane)

Check SMCP status in istio-system namespace

Confirm it is in Ready state with no errors

3) Validate SMMR (Service Mesh Member Roll)

Verify smmr resource exists

Ensure required namespaces are listed under members

4) Create Namespace

Create a new namespace for deployment

5) Add Namespace to Mesh (only if missing)

Edit SMMR and add namespace to members

Skip if already present

6) Render MicroStrategy YAML

Generate deployment YAML using Helm/script/template

Validate configuration before applying

7) Apply MicroStrategy Environment


8) Ensure all components are created

